1
00:00:00,160 --> 00:00:03,160
I've been hiding my true feelings all this time.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:06,040
Unable to speak my heart.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:09,000
But,

4
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:12,560
Always by your side,

5
00:00:13,880 --> 00:00:15,800
Looking up to you,

6
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:19,720
I realized I can no longer lie to myself.

7
00:00:26,240 --> 00:00:28,240
I can't fit into this glass slipper.

8
00:00:32,720 --> 00:00:34,360
Even so,

9
00:00:36,360 --> 00:00:38,720
I still love you from the bottom of my heart.

10
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:43,200
Though Cinderella is nowhere to be found,

11
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,400
Yet,

12
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:46,200
The attendant who stayed by the prince's side,

13
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,880
Finally reveals his hidden affection.

14
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:59,000
I am who I am.

15
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:02,160
Your brother, not by blood.

16
00:01:02,440 --> 00:01:03,440
I have feelings for you...

17
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:26,920
Under the power of magic,

18
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:30,720
The prince realized his true love,

19
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:36,060
And stayed with his attendant forever.

20
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:42,580
What a happy ending.

21
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:57,400
Congratulations!

22
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,280
Reality is different from fiction after all.

23
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:05,720
The intensity of falling in love,

24
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,120
It's nothing like I imagined.

25
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:13,660
Hiding your heart,

26
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:15,900
You might forget your true feelings for a while,

27
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:19,220
But what matters most is...

28
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:20,860
Kono Mizuki!

29
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:23,540
Let's take a picture together!

30
00:02:24,740 --> 00:02:26,700
Staying true to yourself.

31
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:30,300
Ready, here I go!

32
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:43,580
Let's take a group photo!

33
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:50,340
Here we go!

34
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:57,340
Is the timer showing up?

35
00:02:57,820 --> 00:02:59,620
Yes! It's there!

36
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:01,780
Hurry up and get over here!

37
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:13,160
Did you both pack all your bags?

38
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,600
- I've told you a dozen times.
- We've got everything.

39
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:18,600
Make sure you get along with Iijima Hinata!

40
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:22,120
Living together will save on rent and food!

41
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,240
Take care!

42
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,600
We're off!

43
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:34,000
It's great that we got into the same university.

44
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,200
Only because I tutored you.

45
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:40,320
You were the one who said we'd move out after graduation!

46
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:42,160
Weren't you the one who insisted on coming along?
